## Development

```bash
# Clone the repo
gh repo clone tomdyson/toktab-cli
cd toktab-cli

# Install with dev dependencies
uv venv
source .venv/bin/activate
uv pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest

# Test locally
toktab gpt-4o
```

